                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="card">
                                <figure class="card__thumb">
                                    <img src="/media/curacao_flag.png"
                                        alt="Picture by Nathan Dumlao" class="card__image">
                                    <figcaption class="card__caption">
                                        <h2 class="card__title">Papiamentu</h2>
                                        <p class="card__snippet">Kontentu ku bo kier inskribí pa e kurso di piano. E methodo Akort!
